data.title: About: Dolores Guinness
data.meta_description: Dolores Guinness (31 July 1936 – 20 January 2012) was a German-born "Freiin" (Baroness), socialite, fashion icon and jet set member of the 1950s and 1960s. She has been a member of the International Best Dressed List since 1970. Her mother was the Mexican-born socialite Gloria Guinness.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

دولوريس غونس (بالألمانية: Dolores Guinness)‏ هي نجمة اجتماعية ألمانية، ولدت في 31 يوليو 1936 في تشارلوتنبرغ في ألمانيا، وتوفيت في 20 يناير 2012 في لوزان في سويسرا. (ar)

Dolores Guinness (31 July 1936 – 20 January 2012) was a German-born "Freiin" (Baroness), socialite, fashion icon and jet set member of the 1950s and 1960s. She has been a member of the International Best Dressed List since 1970. Her mother was the Mexican-born socialite Gloria Guinness. (en)
